c129","tid":404734,"uid":34929,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"唔係大聲就好戲架路飛<br />\n尤其是最嬲尾果句我要打飛你果句呀<br />\n你嗌到幾硬幾假呀 盲既都知你做緊戲啦"},{"pid":"2466380df62d822bdc8ff60327fea3cb43cadae1","tid":404734,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實冇咁差<br />\n但以依家呢個標準<br />\n以前好多漫畫都唔算好睇</blockquote><br />\n例如?</blockquote><br />\n龍珠依家先連載既話你估仲有冇咁多人睇?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海賊王家陣已經可以同龍珠睇齊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同一道理姐</blockquote><br />\n畫功 劇情 搞笑完勝海賊王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9f17d733ac80002a378f0c128af52def7387b4","tid":404734,"uid":28435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"兒童向"},{"pid":"38f14a8897b159e947274e08c4b1c84420ba0d77","tid":404734,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"拖得太長<br />\n而家都係無聊先睇幾集<br />\n<br />\n追下龍珠超好過"},{"pid":"ba540b15c87204c5bf2378182784b557d45db073","tid":404734,"uid":80598,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:38:35.000Z","msg":"FA故事完整，結構又嚴謹<br />\n除咗終極Boss之外嘅打鬥因為基於鍊金術之上，所以唔會差距太大<br />\n打鬥模式set死咗唔會太強/太弱，所以大部份打鬥都好正<br />\n同埋馬斯丹、大總統真係好型棍<br />\n<br />\n拎海賊王同FA比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a96e11dce581c46fca7c1b8802330f68da82ea9","tid":404734,"uid":102938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"以前覺得好好睇<br />\n一開始出道其實幾悶，係魚人先開始好睇小小<br />\n直至去到打沙惡魚果到記憶猶新<br />\n真係為左救公主救國家而單憑幾人之力再拉國王軍打爆成個沙惡國家<br />\n好啦之後到CP9真係最熱血，救羅賓果到睇到真係好感動<br />\n之後既篇章都OK，到艾斯死後之前既篇章，其實覺得都仲接受到<br />\n自從明哥果到開始，我覺得根本唔似睇緊海賊王<br />\n無哂以前果種熱血感覺同戰鬥場面既刺激感&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n所以我睇到打爆明哥果到開始已經無再點追<br />\n唉以前係個個星期等追海賊，近兩三年都無了<br />\n相反火影選擇完結係正確，至少有個美好回憶同結局完左"},{"pid":"ce515abe5255af505b30055aee782f3fe121028b","tid":404734,"uid":37890,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"現充偽毒咪成日吹奏呢D垃圾話好睇囉<br />\n食開屎點知咩叫好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f748732e7d3b8edf7c38e3d4d9b1ef9147467f","tid":404734,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實冇咁差<br />\n但以依家呢個標準<br />\n以前好多漫畫都唔算好睇</blockquote><br />\n例如?</blockquote><br />\n龍珠依家先連載既話你估仲有冇咁多人睇?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海賊王家陣已經可以同龍珠睇齊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同一道理姐</blockquote><br />\n畫功 劇情 搞笑完勝海賊王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫功認同<br />\n搞笑唔多覺<br />\n計打鬥就龍珠好睇好多，呢點不嬲係海賊既弱項<br />\n但戲情就兩套一擔擔，又係極之公式，op可能仲多啲花臣"},{"pid":"08d382c52a1f71dd0dc0de2e3e8490db36223503","tid":404734,"uid":136345,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"睇完第一集 路飛係個桶度爆出黎就無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465efdbda88fe883569a1f9ed8e16244b52dc8c3","tid":404734,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"而家有好睇過 而家的確唔好睇"},{"pid":"e08b642d34dafb136f06b459d470ad45860f43aa","tid":404734,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現充偽毒咪成日吹奏呢D垃圾話好睇囉<br />\n食開屎點知咩叫好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s